## Quick Reference

### Invocation

**Fresh start:**
```
Fix linting using /midtempo-framework/setup-skills/fix-linting.md
```

**Continue batch:**
```
Continue fix-linting batch [N] using /midtempo-framework/setup-skills/fix-linting.md
```

### Commands

```bash
{{ "lint" | cmd }}         # Run linting
{% if commands.lint_fix is defined %}
{{ "lint_fix" | cmd }}     # Auto-fix where possible
{% endif %}
{{ "test" | cmd }}         # Verify tests pass
```

### Progress File

`planning/lint-fix-progress.md`

### Required Configuration by Linter

**ESLint (TypeScript/JavaScript):**
```json
{
  "rules": {
    "max-lines-per-function": ["error", { "max": 75 }],
    "complexity": ["error", 10],
    "max-lines": ["error", { "max": 500 }],
    "max-depth": ["error", 4],
    "max-params": ["error", 5],
    "no-nested-ternary": "error"
  }
}
```

**Pylint (Python):**
```ini
[DESIGN]
max-args=5
max-locals=15
max-branches=10
max-statements=50

[FORMAT]
max-module-lines=500
max-line-length=100
```

**Ruff (Python):**
```toml
[tool.ruff.pylint]
max-args = 5
max-branches = 10
max-statements = 50
```

